file.name: SwaggerDef.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Backend API definition
  version: 1.0.0

components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer

security :
  - bearerAuth: []
  
paths:
  /bookings:
    get:
      summary: Get all bookings
      tags: 
        - Booking
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A JSON body with stored booking details
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type : object
                properties:
                  bookings:
                    type: array
                    description : Booking detail array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      description : Booking items
                      properties:
                        ref-id:
                          type: string
                          description : Reference id of the entity
                        driver:
                          type: string
                          description : Name of the dirver
                        client:
                          type: string
                          description : Name of the client
                        client-phone:
                          type: string
                          description : Client phone number
    post:
      summary: Insert a booking
      tags: 
        - Booking
      requestBody:
        description: Request body
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type : object
              properties:
                driver:
                  type: string
                  description : Name of the dirver
                client:
                  type: string
                  description : Name of the client
                client-phone:
                  type: string
                  description : Client phone number
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A JSON body with stored bookings
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type : object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
                    description : Status ok
                  ref-id:
                    type: string
                    description : Reference id of the entity
        '5XX':
          description: A JSON body with error details
          content :
            application/json:
              schema:
                type : object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
                    description : Status fail
                  error-code:
                    type: string
                    description : Error code from server

Error: notImplemented: path "/bookings": post: responses: HTTP code pattern not implemented
